collection.name: (B)APETAVERSE
collection.description: (B)APETAVERSE is virtual universe where BAPEFAMs get together to elevate the purpose of collectibles to a new level. Conceptualized from the official A BATHING APE®️, The King of Apes will headline (B)APETAVERSE and unveil his face for the first time. These uniquely high-quality 3D designed NFTs will help members to unlock future exclusive perks, drops, raffles, content and more.
